@inherits AdminComponentBase

<Overview3Cols>
    <Text1>
        <strong>MCP Server</strong> provides a Model Context Protocol endpoint that enables AI assistants to interact with Proxmox VE environments.<br />
        Users can connect their AI tools (Claude, ChatGPT, etc.) to query cluster status, manage VMs, and automate infrastructure tasks.<br />
        The server exposes Proxmox operations through a standardized protocol that AI assistants can understand and utilize.
    </Text1>
    <Text2>
        <strong>AI-Powered Management</strong>: Users can manage Proxmox infrastructure through natural language commands via AI assistants.<br />
        <strong>Real-time Data Access</strong>: AI tools can query VM status, cluster health, resource usage, and configuration details.<br />
        <strong>Automated Operations</strong>: Enable AI assistants to perform routine tasks like VM management, snapshot creation, and monitoring.<br />
        <strong>Standardized Protocol</strong>: Uses Model Context Protocol for consistent AI integration across different platforms.<br />
    </Text2>
    <Text3>
        <strong>Easy Integration</strong>: Simple setup allows users to connect their preferred AI assistants to Proxmox environments.<br />
        <strong>Secure Access</strong>: Controlled API exposure ensures safe interaction between AI tools and critical infrastructure.<br />
        <strong>Enhanced Productivity</strong>: Transform complex Proxmox operations into simple conversational interactions with AI.<br />
    </Text3>
</Overview3Cols>
